title: Got the icon and kayle, but no skin
body:
This is to riot, or anyone that can help me out, but I got the summoner icon and kayle today, however I did not get riot skin kayle. I know the deadline for the second pass was yesterday, so I was just wondering when I would get it. 

Danke, 
Radnar the bold

replies.body: The gifts are sent out separately, so some players may not receive everything all at once.  Per our current [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-), we're still distributing these gifts.  The goodies will be coming with just a little more time!

The gifts are still being distributed, and the final date to receive them has been pushed back to the 30th as per the banner on the [support page](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us). Just hang tight!
